name: Little Parrot brooch
description:
Wooden brooches are made by hand in Castlemaine Victoria.
The timber comes from the fallen branches of Eucalypt trees. Each piece has it's unique characteristics, carefully crafted to bring out the natural beauty of the timber. Each brooch design is made to reflect native birds and plants that make their home amongst these beautiful trees. Brooches can be fastened to clothing and headwear  by a clasp pin on the back.
